==迴響及後續==
時任[[俄罗斯总统|俄罗斯总统]][[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|德米特里·梅德韦杰夫]]擔心修憲將令「國家陷落」，最終令極端主義政黨掌權<ref name="Russia Snubs New Kyrgyzstan Constitution">{{cite news|author=Volkov, Andrey|url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/content/view/38231/|title=Russia Snubs New Kyrgyzstan Constitution|date=2010-06-28|work=[[大纪元时报|The Epoch Times]]|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-date=2010-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101018015224/http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/content/view/38231/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國國務院則讚揚公投，並呼籲臨時政府及吉國人民「推進和解和問責，確保種族間未來都可和平，帶領吉爾吉斯邁向穩定、安全、民主和繁榮穩定」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bishkek.usembassy.gov/2010_0628_dos_on_referendum.html |title=2010_0628_Dos_on_Referendum - U.S. Embassy Bishkek, Kyrgyz Republic |publisher=美國駐比什凱克大使館 |date=2010-06-28 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721071511/http://bishkek.usembassy.gov/2010_0628_dos_on_referendum.html |archivedate=2011-07-21 |accessdate=2020-11-17 }}</ref>。

改制後的首場[[2010年吉爾吉斯國會選舉|國會選舉]]在同年舉行，國會獲賦予更多權力，最終由提倡改行舊制和歡迎巴基耶夫回國的[[故乡_(政党)|故鄉黨]]取得不過半數的最多議席<ref name="analysis">{{cite web|title=Kyrgyzstan election results may lead to further instability|url=http://www.allvoices.com/contributed-news/6995706-kyrgyzstan-election-results-may-lead-to-further-instability|accessdate=2010-10-12|publisher=Allvoices.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313122846/http://www.allvoices.com/contributed-news/6995706-kyrgyzstan-election-results-may-lead-to-further-instability|archivedate=2012-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

